The Ant System:
Optimization by a colony of cooperating agents

{{paper ant/IJ.10-SMC96.pdf}}

{{category 1996}}
{{category ACO}}
{{category Ant System}}

Marco Dorigo*,^, Member, IEEE, Vittorio Maniezzo%,^, and Alberto Colorni#

